Description
       ProductSecurity Engineer
       Are youinterested in working on security at one of biggest global
       internet companies?Be a part of a dynamic team that Yahoo! provides
       a safe and securityenvironment for all of its users. We are looking
       for a range of skilledsecurity engineers to help secure new
       products as they launch and reviewexisting platforms and
       properties. Candidates should have a strongunderstanding of
       software development and how to build secure web applicationsat
       scale.
       Requirements
       - 2 yearsof relevant work experience in the internet security
       industry
       - must have hands-on experience developing or supporting
       largescalable web based solutions
       - strong understanding of networking, protocols and how theinternet
       works
       - strong communication skills
       - solid scripting skills in one of the
       following:PHP/Perl/Python/Ruby using UNIX
